##As Qingming nears, Shanghai launches Internet Memorial Day Sweep and Book Memorial Day sweep

“

Since the outbreak of the epidemic, Shanghai funeral service places, the overall decline of more than 70 percent.

”

Funeral places providing services for relatives and friends to send off, bury and sweep the dead have become the key places for epidemic prevention and control due to the characteristics of gathering of people and dense flow of people. After the outbreak, funeral service units such as Shanghai Funeral Parlors, cemeteries and Columbaria did not hold wake, public farewell, public sacrifice and memorial services, as well as gathering activities for burial at sea and other personnel.

On the afternoon of March 14, Zeng Qun, deputy director general of the Shanghai Municipal Bureau of Civil Affairs, said that since the outbreak of the epidemic, the overall flow of people to funeral services in Shanghai has dropped by more than 70 percent.

Zeng urged the general public not to go to the cemetery or the hall of ashes during this year's Qingming Festival. To this end, the civil affairs department will also introduce three convenience measures: during the Qingming Festival this year (March 28 to April 12) , the city-wide operating cemeteries (Columbaria) will introduce three convenience measures, namely collective offering, Internet offering and proxy offering.

"Collective Memorial" means that each cemetery will hold a collective memorial ceremony for the deceased buried in the park during the Qingming Festival "Online memorial service" means that each cemetery will open a "online memorial service platform" on its own official website or wechat public account. Citizens can log in through their computers or mobile phones to pay their respects to their loved ones. "paying tribute to visitors" means that the public will not go to the scene, to entrust the cemetery to pay tribute to their loved ones, the cemetery will arrange staff to provide services such as cleaning tombstones, bowing and presenting flowers, and feed back the service process to the public through photos. Of the three services, the first two are free; the "Valet Sweep" will be appropriately charged, but all prices will be announced, the most basic package price of 35 yuan.

Secondly, taking into account that during the Qingming Festival, some residents really have a need for burial, and some residents really have reasons to need on-site memorial sweeping, Shanghai will implement the practice of "making an appointment for burial" and "making an appointment for memorial sweeping" .

Zeng Qun said that "scheduled burial" should strictly control the number of participants, each family no more than 10 people. In addition, it is also acceptable to collect and deposit ashes at funeral parlours or Columbaria during the Ching Ming Festival. However, members of the public are advised to check with the funeral parlours or Columbaria concerned on the points to note and procedures, and make an appointment registration in advance.

For individual "scheduled memorial sweeping" , Shanghai will adopt by the operating cemetery, Ashes Hall "Limited appointment, until the expiration of the appointment, time-sharing memorial sweeping" measures. Booking starts on March 26.

On the sacrifices and the prevention and control of the epidemic during this year's Qingming Festival, the Civil Affairs Department will also inform the public in a timely manner through various channels, such as the wechat public number "published in Shanghai" , the website "Shanghai Funeral Service Platform" , rolling captions on TV and short messages on mobile phones, so as to expand the public's awareness. The funeral service units will also through their own channels, timely notification of relevant information to customers.

Zeng Qun stressed that starting from this year's Qingming Festival, funeral service units throughout the city will strictly implement "smoke-free sacrificial sweeping, " And further promote the "simple funeral, ecological burial, Home Nostalgia, network sacrificial sweeping, flowers sacrificial sweeping, " and other funeral civilization new fashion. He also called on the general public to further change their views, jointly promote the reform of funeral customs, and constantly promote the changing of funeral and burial customs.

"We urge the general public to continue to understand, support and cooperate with the above-mentioned measures we have taken during the Qingming Festival this year, so as to contribute to the early victory of the epidemic prevention and control campaign, " Zeng said.
